00:11:14.141 --> 00:11:15.809 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Bel, are you all right?

00:11:15.943 --> 00:11:17.512 position:35% line:83% align:start
[BELZEBUTH]
Yes, my lord.

00:11:17.646 --> 00:11:19.680 position:7% line:89% align:start
Then let us hurry, we're late.

00:11:23.050 --> 00:11:24.553 position:24% line:83% align:start
What is the meaning
of this, CÃ©dric?

00:11:24.685 --> 00:11:27.388 position:10% line:83% align:start
You dare invite a guest only
to wrongly detain them?

00:11:27.522 --> 00:11:28.689 position:27% line:89% align:start
