00:11:37.097 --> 00:11:38.933 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Neither Lilia's
whereabouts nor the letters

00:11:39.066 --> 00:11:40.234 position:13% line:89% align:start
have a thing to do with me.

00:11:40.367 --> 00:11:41.869 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you're so certain
I'm the culprit,

00:11:42.002 --> 00:11:43.470 position:16% line:89% align:start
then where's your proof?

00:11:43.605 --> 00:11:45.272 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CÃDRIC] Ha! Who else would
be vindictive enough

00:11:45.406 --> 00:11:46.740 position:24% line:89% align:start
to do such a thing?

00:11:46.874 --> 00:11:48.242 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] You've caused all
this commotion without a lick

00:11:48.375 --> 00:11:49.777 position:33% line:89% align:start
of evidence?

00:11:49.910 --> 00:11:52.614 position:7% line:83% align:start
Ah! I'm often perplexed by how
I could've ever fallen in love

00:11:52.746 --> 00:11:54.181 position:10% line:89% align:start
with a man such as yourself.

00:11:54.315 --> 00:11:56.217 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't utter these
remarks you don't mean!

00:11:56.350 --> 00:11:58.252 position:21% line:83% align:start
You did this because
Lilia stands in the way

00:11:58.385 --> 00:11:59.720 position:30% line:89% align:start
of our reunion!

00:11:59.853 --> 00:12:02.823 position:5% line:83% align:start
Bleh! I'd rather be pitched to
the void than reunite with you.

00:12:02.957 --> 00:12:04.526 position:33% line:89% align:start
Au contraire!

00:12:04.659 --> 00:12:06.227 position:7% line:83% align:start
Did you think I would be quick
to forget your pitiful cries

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:07.629 position:33% line:89% align:start
of adoration?

00:12:07.761 --> 00:12:08.996 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:12:09.763 --> 00:12:11.966 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Prince CÃ©dric.

00:12:12.099 --> 00:12:14.301 position:19% line:89% align:start
I truly did adore you.

00:12:14.435 --> 00:12:17.238 position:16% line:83% align:start
Was it your intention to
ignore my use of past tense?

00:12:17.371 --> 00:12:18.939 position:27% line:89% align:start
I did adore you.

00:12:19.073 --> 00:12:20.374 position:30% line:89% align:start
But no longer.

00:12:20.508 --> 00:12:23.210 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have come to despise
the very thought of you.

00:12:23.344 --> 00:12:26.313 position:13% line:83% align:start
My affections of old have
entirely ceased to linger.

00:12:26.447 --> 00:12:28.516 position:10% line:83% align:start
In fact, give me the document
and I'll be more than happy

00:12:28.650 --> 00:12:31.720 position:10% line:83% align:start
to expedite the nullification
