00:12:34.188 --> 00:12:35.624 position:41% line:83% align:start
[ISAAC]
Too far, Aileen.

00:12:35.756 --> 00:12:37.358 position:7% line:89% align:start
You're provoking him too much.

00:12:37.491 --> 00:12:39.293 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CÃDRIC]
You say you despise me.

00:12:39.426 --> 00:12:41.028 position:30% line:89% align:start
Is that so? Ha!

00:12:41.161 --> 00:12:43.030 position:10% line:89% align:start
Tell the good people, Aileen!

00:12:43.163 --> 00:12:45.766 position:21% line:83% align:start
That you'll never be
able to move on.

00:12:45.899 --> 00:12:47.669 position:30% line:83% align:start
--[CROWD gasps]
--Obey me!

00:12:47.801 --> 00:12:50.971 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you confess your love
and admit your vengeful plot,

00:12:51.105 --> 00:12:53.307 position:10% line:89% align:start
perhaps I'll show you mercy!

00:12:55.009 --> 00:12:56.343 position:19% line:89% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric, please!

00:12:56.477 --> 00:12:59.013 position:16% line:83% align:start
[SOLDIER B] You shouldn't
use such force on a lady!

00:12:59.146 --> 00:13:02.383 position:21% line:83% align:start
Silence! She was my
woman to begin with!

00:13:02.517 --> 00:13:03.817 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ISAAC sighs]

00:13:03.951 --> 00:13:05.520 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door opens]

00:13:05.654 --> 00:13:07.288 position:33% line:83% align:start
[MESSENGER A]
I'm sorry to interrupt,

00:13:07.421 --> 00:13:09.290 position:19% line:83% align:start
but I bear an important
message for Prince CÃ©dric.

00:13:09.423 --> 00:13:11.859 position:21% line:83% align:start
It will have to wait!
I'm rather busy!

00:13:11.992 --> 00:13:13.794 position:24% line:89% align:start
But Prince Claude.

00:13:15.029 --> 00:13:16.930 position:27% line:89% align:start
He's-- he's here!

00:13:17.064 --> 00:13:19.099 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CÃDRIC gasps]

00:13:24.171 --> 00:13:27.074 position:19% line:89% align:start
[GUESTS gasp, chatter]

00:13:36.518 --> 00:13:37.918 position:33% line:89% align:start
Could it be?

00:13:50.732 --> 00:13:52.099 position:38% line:89% align:start
Brother?

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:14.054 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's repaired?

00:14:14.188 --> 00:14:15.757 position:10% line:89% align:start
That must be the demon lord!

00:14:15.889 --> 00:14:17.559 position:19% line:89% align:start
Did he just use magic?

00:14:17.692 --> 00:14:19.828 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've never seen it before!

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:22.863 position:13% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] CÃ©dric, were you
the fool who sent soldiers

00:14:22.996 --> 00:14:23.931 position:33% line:89% align:start
to my forest?

00:14:24.064 --> 00:14:26.233 position:33% line:89% align:start
Well, I, uh--

00:14:26.367 --> 00:14:30.137 position:10% line:83% align:start
Your miniscule band couldn't
lay a finger on my castle.

00:14:30.270 --> 00:14:32.373 position:7% line:89% align:start
I had them dealt with swiftly.

00:14:34.308 --> 00:14:37.311 position:7% line:83% align:start
As crown prince, you shouldn't
act so thoughtlessly.

00:14:37.444 --> 00:14:39.781 position:19% line:83% align:start
Don't provide me with a
reason to burn this country

00:14:39.913 --> 00:14:41.516 position:30% line:89% align:start
to the ground.

00:14:43.050 --> 00:14:44.952 position:27% line:89% align:start
I made you wait.

00:14:45.085 --> 00:14:46.320 position:24% line:89% align:start
Apologies, madame.

00:14:46.453 --> 00:14:47.388 position:33% line:89% align:start
Heavens, no.

00:14:47.522 --> 00:14:49.557 position:30% line:83% align:start
I only arrived
a short while ago.

00:14:49.691 --> 00:14:51.125 position:24% line:89% align:start
You wore the dress.

00:14:51.258 --> 00:14:53.327 position:30% line:83% align:start
I knew it would
look nice on you.

00:14:55.496 --> 00:14:57.665 position:35% line:89% align:start
What? Him?

00:14:57.799 --> 00:14:59.500 position:16% line:89% align:start
Tell me that it isn't so.

00:14:59.634 --> 00:15:01.435 position:27% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] Have you
signed the nullification?

00:15:01.569 --> 00:15:02.837 position:21% line:89% align:start
Not yet, I'm afraid.

00:15:02.970 --> 00:15:04.639 position:5% line:89% align:start
Finalize it as soon as possible.

00:15:04.773 --> 00:15:09.410 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'd prefer not to escort my
younger brother's fiancÃ©e.

00:15:09.544 --> 00:15:10.911 position:33% line:89% align:start
Wait, Aileen!

00:15:11.044 --> 00:15:13.180 position:16% line:89% align:start
You swear it wasn't you?

00:15:13.313 --> 00:15:16.016 position:24% line:83% align:start
You didn't steal my
Lilia away from me?

00:15:17.217 --> 00:15:20.722 position:19% line:83% align:start
I felt as though I had
made that perfectly clear.

00:15:20.855 --> 00:15:22.189 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh...?

00:15:22.322 --> 00:15:24.491 position:24% line:83% align:start
Who else would have
any reason to take her?

00:15:31.833 --> 00:15:33.300 position:16% line:89% align:start
No matter how hard I try,

00:15:33.434 --> 00:15:35.804 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can never beat my
big brother at anything.

00:15:35.936 --> 00:15:37.605 position:27% line:89% align:start
That isn't true.

00:15:37.739 --> 00:15:38.972 position:41% line:89% align:start
It is!

00:15:39.106 --> 00:15:40.675 position:21% line:83% align:start
They all laugh about
it behind my back.

00:15:42.443 --> 00:15:44.344 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] I spent a lot of
my childhood suffering from

00:15:44.478 --> 00:15:47.047 position:24% line:83% align:start
endless comparison
to my older brothers.

00:15:48.449 --> 00:15:51.251 position:19% line:83% align:start
I wish I had told him I
was on his side back then.

00:15:51.385 --> 00:15:53.721 position:24% line:83% align:start
Maybe things would
be different now.

00:15:53.855 --> 00:15:55.055 position:41% line:89% align:start
Isaac.

00:16:00.595 --> 00:16:03.565 position:10% line:83% align:start
This is one of the infamous
letters Lady Lilia received.

00:16:03.698 --> 00:16:05.733 position:13% line:83% align:start
A generous friend of mine
was able to fish it out of

00:16:05.867 --> 00:16:07.000 position:33% line:89% align:start
your rubbish.

00:16:07.134 --> 00:16:08.736 position:13% line:89% align:start
What exactly is your point?

00:16:08.870 --> 00:16:11.171 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] The letters were
written on a special stationery

00:16:11.305 --> 00:16:14.208 position:13% line:89% align:start
the Lombard Company makes.

00:16:14.341 --> 00:16:17.010 position:21% line:83% align:start
The sheets are glued
together into 20-page pads.

00:16:17.144 --> 00:16:19.279 position:16% line:83% align:start
After adhesion, the rose
design at the bottom

00:16:19.413 --> 00:16:22.249 position:21% line:83% align:start
is cut out of all the
pages simultaneously.

00:16:22.382 --> 00:16:26.119 position:19% line:83% align:start
Knowing this, let's say
we overlap two pages.

00:16:26.253 --> 00:16:27.822 position:24% line:83% align:start
If they originate
from the same pad,

00:16:27.956 --> 00:16:29.524 position:5% line:89% align:start
the roses will line up exactly.

00:16:29.657 --> 00:16:32.192 position:16% line:83% align:start
If they're from different
pads, they will not.

00:16:33.862 --> 00:16:35.797 position:24% line:83% align:start
In one hand, I have
the threatening letter;

00:16:35.930 --> 00:16:38.265 position:7% line:83% align:start
in the other, a note that Lady
Lilia sent me along with

00:16:38.398 --> 00:16:40.602 position:30% line:83% align:start
the invitation
to tonight's ball.

00:16:45.372 --> 00:16:47.241 position:30% line:89% align:start
[CÃDRIC gasps]

00:16:48.475 --> 00:16:51.445 position:16% line:83% align:start
The two letters come from
the same pad of stationery.

00:16:51.579 --> 00:16:53.982 position:16% line:83% align:start
Put simply, the harrowing
letters that have caused

00:16:54.114 --> 00:16:57.017 position:10% line:83% align:start
your beloved so much anguish
had to have been penned

00:16:57.150 --> 00:16:58.753 position:27% line:89% align:start
by her own hand.

00:16:59.888 --> 00:17:01.923 position:24% line:83% align:start
I suppose I should
leave this with you.

00:17:02.055 --> 00:17:05.392 position:7% line:83% align:start
After all, it doesn't have the
slightest thing to do with me.

00:17:09.229 --> 00:17:12.534 position:30% line:83% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric,
I must bid you adieu.

00:17:12.667 --> 00:17:15.570 position:13% line:83% align:start
I hope you and sweet Lilia
find much happiness.

00:17:26.881 --> 00:17:28.382 position:30% line:89% align:start
Exquisite work.

00:17:32.754 --> 00:17:35.422 position:21% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] When I was a
little girl, you filled me with

00:17:35.557 --> 00:17:38.158 position:7% line:83% align:start
the glimmer of confidence and
courage I had been waiting for

00:17:38.292 --> 00:17:39.827 position:30% line:89% align:start
my whole life.

00:17:40.862 --> 00:17:42.564 position:13% line:89% align:start
It pushed me to work hard.

00:17:44.231 --> 00:17:47.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
Though I lost a lot
becoming who I am,

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:49.504 position:27% line:83% align:start
I like to think I
gained even more.

00:17:56.911 --> 00:17:59.479 position:30% line:83% align:start
I might've been
Prince CÃ©dric's fiancÃ©e,

00:17:59.614 --> 00:18:02.650 position:19% line:83% align:start
but I never really felt
like I was his love.

00:18:02.784 --> 00:18:03.818 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows.

00:18:03.952 --> 00:18:06.486 position:24% line:83% align:start
Maybe I'll miss my
comrade-in-arms someday.

00:18:09.356 --> 00:18:10.925 position:33% line:89% align:start
But not now.

00:18:11.059 --> 00:18:13.126 position:19% line:89% align:start
Goodbye, Prince CÃ©dric.

00:18:22.036 --> 00:18:23.504 position:35% line:89% align:start
Well done.

00:18:23.638 --> 00:18:26.507 position:19% line:83% align:start
And now that you are no
longer bound to another man,

00:18:26.641 --> 00:18:28.375 position:21% line:83% align:start
will you grant me the
honor of your first dance

00:18:28.509 --> 00:18:30.044 position:24% line:89% align:start
as your own woman?

00:18:30.177 --> 00:18:32.547 position:7% line:89% align:start
Lady Aileen Lauren d'Autriche?

00:18:44.191 --> 00:18:47.895 position:16% line:89% align:start
Funny. Hilarious, I say!

00:18:48.029 --> 00:18:49.864 position:19% line:89% align:start
She chose him over me?

00:18:51.966 --> 00:18:55.302 position:10% line:83% align:start
I can't believe you betrayed
me, you miserable girl.

00:18:55.435 --> 00:18:58.506 position:19% line:83% align:start
Mark my words, you will
not get away with this!

00:19:06.547 --> 00:19:08.650 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Thank you for an amazing night.

00:19:08.783 --> 00:19:11.451 position:21% line:83% align:start
I hear that the lost
lady has been found.

00:19:11.586 --> 00:19:13.453 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's a shame Prince
CÃ©dric couldn't announce

00:19:13.588 --> 00:19:15.489 position:24% line:83% align:start
their engagement at
the ball, but at least his

00:19:15.623 --> 00:19:19.093 position:27% line:83% align:start
soon-to-be bride
is safely at home.

00:19:19.226 --> 00:19:20.795 position:5% line:89% align:start
You played a role in this, yes?

00:19:20.928 --> 00:19:22.664 position:35% line:89% align:start
Pardon me?

00:19:22.797 --> 00:19:24.832 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] It was almost as if
Lady Lilia had been magically

00:19:24.966 --> 00:19:27.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
transported to some
unknown forest.

00:19:30.538 --> 00:19:32.540 position:10% line:89% align:start
She's quite a beautiful girl.

00:19:33.541 --> 00:19:35.143 position:24% line:89% align:start
Wouldn't you agree?

00:19:35.275 --> 00:19:36.678 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Crap.

00:19:36.811 --> 00:19:38.780 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well that's definitely not
what I wanted to say.

00:19:38.913 --> 00:19:41.248 position:21% line:83% align:start
Right? She's the most
popular lady around.

00:19:41.381 --> 00:19:43.051 position:5% line:89% align:start
They say her smile heals souls.

00:19:43.183 --> 00:19:46.587 position:7% line:83% align:start
Her skin is just flawless, and
her hair is perfectly smooth.

00:19:46.721 --> 00:19:49.389 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] What am I doing?
I can't stop!

00:19:49.524 --> 00:19:51.125 position:16% line:89% align:start
...known for her honesty.

00:19:51.258 --> 00:19:53.127 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Aileen.

00:19:53.260 --> 00:19:55.530 position:27% line:83% align:start
I don't see what
you're so afraid of.

00:19:58.733 --> 00:20:00.434 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Lilia is the heroine.

00:20:00.568 --> 00:20:02.469 position:16% line:83% align:start
All she has to do is say
the phrase from the game

00:20:02.603 --> 00:20:05.773 position:24% line:83% align:start
to trigger a route,
depending on what chooses.

00:20:07.141 --> 00:20:08.976 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Ouch!

00:20:09.110 --> 00:20:12.245 position:13% line:83% align:start
It has a greater plasticity
than I anticipated.

00:20:12.379 --> 00:20:13.447 position:30% line:89% align:start
[AILEEN grunts]

00:20:13.581 --> 00:20:16.483 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's an odd way to comfort!

00:20:16.617 --> 00:20:19.319 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's no need to worry
about me diverting my gaze.

00:20:19.453 --> 00:20:21.856 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're pretty and she's
not my cup of tea.

00:20:25.059 --> 00:20:26.861 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, that's nice to hear.

00:20:28.162 --> 00:20:31.165 position:19% line:83% align:start
So what did you the two
of you talk about, anyway?

00:20:31.298 --> 00:20:32.767 position:24% line:89% align:start
Nothing memorable.

00:20:32.900 --> 00:20:34.869 position:13% line:83% align:start
If I recall, she mentioned
something about being able

00:20:35.002 --> 00:20:36.671 position:27% line:89% align:start
to grant my wish.

00:20:36.804 --> 00:20:38.673 position:10% line:89% align:start
What? How could she do that?

00:20:38.806 --> 00:20:42.009 position:13% line:83% align:start
Your wish is for humans and
demons to live in harmony, yes?

00:20:45.179 --> 00:20:47.280 position:24% line:83% align:start
You looked so happy
watching over your demons

00:20:47.414 --> 00:20:49.550 position:27% line:83% align:start
working together
with Denis's crew.

00:20:51.318 --> 00:20:54.387 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was going to say that my
wish is to see you cry, but...

00:20:54.522 --> 00:20:56.389 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] I've had a great
night; wish denied!

00:20:56.524 --> 00:20:57.725 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
I see.

00:20:57.859 --> 00:20:59.093 position:27% line:89% align:start
How unfortunate.

00:20:59.227 --> 00:21:01.095 position:10% line:89% align:start
Well, you must be exhausted.

00:21:01.229 --> 00:21:02.395 position:27% line:89% align:start
You should rest.

00:21:02.530 --> 00:21:04.932 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Indeed. I will soon-- [gasps]

00:21:07.168 --> 00:21:09.937 position:19% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] I said I'd be
the perfect escort,

00:21:10.071 --> 00:21:13.007 position:13% line:89% align:start
and I am a man of my word.

00:21:13.141 --> 00:21:14.407 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Calm down, Aileen.

00:21:14.542 --> 00:21:16.144 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's just a farewell kiss.

00:21:16.276 --> 00:21:18.579 position:10% line:89% align:start
A perfectly common formality.

00:21:24.819 --> 00:21:26.554 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
I'll destroy them.

00:21:27.855 --> 00:21:30.191 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's what their kind deserves!

00:21:30.323 --> 00:21:35.763 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's not one--not one
measly human worth protecting!

00:21:35.897 --> 00:21:38.866 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll tear every
last human to shreds!

00:21:44.672 --> 00:21:46.707 position:24% line:83% align:start
Have a good night,
and sweet dreams.

00:21:46.841 --> 00:21:48.743 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
I hope you have the same.

00:21:54.347 --> 00:21:56.617 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
It's all coming back.

00:21:56.751 --> 00:22:00.021 position:16% line:83% align:start
I remember the reason why
he loses faith in humanity.

00:22:03.057 --> 00:22:07.829 position:13% line:83% align:start
He's going to be betrayed--
by a human.

00:22:07.962 --> 00:22:10.631 position:24% line:83% align:start
The only human he's
trusted since he was young.

